<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q18_v12" title="Q18_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una clase se plantea la siguiente situación:</p>
    <p>
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>p</m:mi>
        <m:mo> </m:mo>
        <m:mtext>es el</m:mtext>
        <m:mo> </m:mo>
        <m:mn>40</m:mn>
        <m:mo>%</m:mo>
        <m:mo> </m:mo>
        <m:mtext>de</m:mtext>
        <m:mo> </m:mo>
        <m:mi>k</m:mi>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>Para calcular el valor de k a partir de p, una profesora propone multiplicar p por un solo número.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes propuestas permite calcular correctamente k a partir de p?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">Multiplicar p por 0,40.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si p es el 40% de k, entonces p = 0,40k. Despejando, k = p ÷ 0,40 = 2,5p. Por lo tanto, multiplicar p por 0,40 entrega 0,40p, que no es igual a k. Por ejemplo, si p = 8, entonces k = 20, pero 8 × 0,40 = 3,2.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">Multiplicar p por 2,5.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si p es el 40% de k, entonces p = 0,40k. Al despejar, k = p ÷ 0,40 = p × 2,5. Por eso, multiplicar p por 2,5 permite calcular correctamente k a partir de p.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">Multiplicar p por 1,40.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si p es el 40% de k, entonces p = 0,40k y, por lo tanto, k = 2,5p. Multiplicar p por 1,40 entrega 1,40p, que no coincide con k. Por ejemplo, si p = 8, entonces k = 20, pero 8 × 1,40 = 11,2.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">Multiplicar p por 40.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si p es el 40% de k, entonces p = 0,40k y, al despejar, k = 2,5p. Multiplicar p por 40 entrega 40p, que es mucho mayor que k. Por ejemplo, si p = 8, entonces k = 20, pero 8 × 40 = 320.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Traducir el enunciado a una igualdad</strong></p>
            <p>“<m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo> </m:mo><m:mtext>es el</m:mtext><m:mo> </m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo><m:mo> </m:mo><m:mtext>de</m:mtext><m:mo> </m:mo><m:mi>k</m:mi></m:math>” significa:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>p</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,40</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>k</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Despejar <m:math><m:mi>k</m:mi></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>Dividimos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>0,40</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>k</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mi>p</m:mi>
                    <m:mn>0,40</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular el número por el que se multiplica <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0,40</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2,5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>k</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2,5</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>p</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La única propuesta que indica multiplicar <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> por <m:math><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:math> es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificación con un ejemplo</strong></p>
            <p>Si</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>k</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>entonces</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>p</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                  <m:mtext> de </m:mtext>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Para recuperar <m:math><m:mi>k</m:mi></m:math> desde <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2,5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La propuesta correcta es <strong>multiplicar <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> por 2,5</strong>, es decir, la <strong>alternativa B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>